snippet.title: Hockey VR Game - Quest 1 and 2
snippet.description:
Strap on your skates, step up to the blue line and test your skills in the most realistic physics-based hockey simulation available! Try your hand at Target Practice or see how many goals you can score against the AI goalie. Choose between Timed or Shot Count game modes. Play in three different environments. Turn on Shot Assist mode to help you score those breath-taking goals. Upgrade your experience and bring your real hockey stick into the game with our 3d printed controller mount.

Get them now https://www.melcher.ca/hockeyvr
